strings: <voice_0x01001385><se_high>Red: I thought I recognised ya! You're that lot who got the Venus' tear for me, intcha?
<voice_0x01001386><se_high>Red: Fancy seein' you again in a place like this!
<voice_0x01001387><se_low>Yangus: Red! Wot on earth are you doin' 'ere!?

<voice_0x01001388><se_high>Jessica: It's Red, isn't it?
What brings you here?

<voice_0x01001389><se_def>Angelo: You're that friend of Yangus's, aren't you?
What are you doing here?
<voice_0x0100138C><se_high>Red: Well, I 'eard a rumour that there's treasure 'ere. Belonged to that old pirate, Captain Crow.

<voice_0x0100138D><se_high>Red: Mention treasure to me, an' I'm unstoppable!
I can't get enough of it! So I got meself this boat and came on down to see wot I could find.
<voice_0x0100138E><se_high>Red: ...By the looks of ya, you're 'ere for the same reason, eh?

<voice_0x0100138F><se_high>Red: Oh, this could be a bit of a laugh, then!
First one to find it, keeps it!
<voice_0x01001390><se_high>Red: ...In which case, I'd better get a wiggle on! Sure you won't mind givin' me a bit of an 'ead start!

<voice_0x01001391><se_low>Yangus: Oi! Hold yer 'orses!
Ya can't just say all that and then run off!

<voice_0x01001392><se_low>Yangus: An' there are monsters in 'ere, y'know.
Look at ya, goin' off 'alf-cocked on yer own!
You must 'ave a screw loose!
<voice_0x01001393><se_high>Red: Who'd you think you are, underestimatin' me like that!? You should know by now 'ow good I am at creepin' around!

<voice_0x01001394><se_high>Red: Those monsters won't even know I'm in 'ere!
Not like you, you big fat clod'opper!
<voice_0x0100138A><se_low>Morrie: Ciao bella. My name is Morrie. It is a pleasure.
<voice_0x0100138B><se_low>Morrie: But why, per favore, are you here?
